WEBVTT

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:08.959
Don't be scared, don't be scared.

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:15.120
Say, if there were no Longshi Group,

00:01:15.120 --> 00:01:16.560
and no issues with Zhou Honghai,

00:01:17.280 --> 00:01:18.640
could we stay like this forever?

00:01:19.840 --> 00:01:22.040
Every day you read books,

00:01:22.359 --> 00:01:23.159
and I do the cooking.

00:01:23.640 --> 00:01:24.640
I wash the dishes.

00:01:24.640 --> 00:01:25.560
I mop the floors.

00:01:25.560 --> 00:01:26.239
I do the cooking.

00:01:26.239 --> 00:01:26.959
I wash the dishes.

00:01:28.280 --> 00:01:29.120
I think so.

00:01:34.920 --> 00:01:35.799
My roommate.

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:37.640
She's asking why I haven't gone back to school.

00:01:37.760 --> 00:01:39.000
I'm going to call her back.

00:01:39.280 --> 00:01:39.760
Okay.

00:01:40.040 --> 00:01:41.000
Should I pause it for you?

00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:41.319
No need.

00:01:52.719 --> 00:01:54.439
Why did he choose that specific place?

00:01:57.719 --> 00:01:59.560
Forget it, everywhere is the same.

00:02:00.599 --> 00:02:03.239
As long as we can end this quickly.

00:02:04.760 --> 00:02:05.439
Okay.

00:02:05.959 --> 00:02:08.280
11:30 tonight. Don't tell Chen Fan.

00:02:11.520 --> 00:02:12.319
Chen Fan.

00:02:14.919 --> 00:02:15.719
Chen Fan.

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:19.639
I hope when you wake up,

00:02:20.360 --> 00:02:21.879
all of this will be over.

00:02:50.479 --> 00:02:51.919
Boss Liu, she's here.

00:02:51.919 --> 00:02:53.520
I'll go talk to her. Don't worry.

00:02:53.680 --> 00:02:55.280
I will definitely make her keep her mouth shut.

00:02:57.719 --> 00:02:58.280
What's wrong?

00:02:58.280 --> 00:03:00.280
I don't know what method that girl used,

00:03:00.560 --> 00:03:01.719
but she knows everything now.

00:03:02.240 --> 00:03:03.439
Keep her alive?

00:03:03.840 --> 00:03:04.800
Wait for her to call the police?

00:03:05.280 --> 00:03:06.719
We must deal with this cleanly once and for all.

00:03:07.439 --> 00:03:08.240
What are you doing?

00:03:09.680 --> 00:03:10.159
Do it.

00:03:10.599 --> 00:03:11.039
Remember,

00:03:11.520 --> 00:03:12.560
that bag is very important.

00:03:13.319 --> 00:03:14.240
Boss Liu, you...

00:03:15.800 --> 00:03:16.120
Ah!

00:03:22.560 --> 00:03:23.560
What's the situation?

00:03:24.520 --> 00:03:26.360
You... you two are kidnapping me!

00:03:26.919 --> 00:03:28.479
It's not kidnapping, it's protection.

00:03:31.319 --> 00:03:32.400
Do we have any eggs left at home?

00:03:32.400 --> 00:03:33.680
I think I forgot to ask Brother Liang to buy some.

00:03:33.919 --> 00:03:34.719
Eggs.

00:03:36.400 --> 00:03:37.240
I'm going to take a call.

00:03:37.240 --> 00:03:37.639
Ah, okay.

00:03:48.879 --> 00:03:49.759
Hello, Brother Honghai.

00:03:50.719 --> 00:03:51.680
Listen to my advice.

00:03:52.120 --> 00:03:53.120
You must not get involved.

00:03:53.120 --> 00:03:54.560
Longshi Group's next project...

00:03:55.120 --> 00:03:56.960
it's not some overseas trade cooperation at all.

00:03:57.319 --> 00:03:58.319
It's smuggling.

00:03:58.759 --> 00:04:00.319
They are smuggling human organs.

00:04:02.919 --> 00:04:04.199
Don't worry about how I know.

00:04:04.319 --> 00:04:05.479
Anyway, I wouldn't lie to you.

00:04:05.960 --> 00:04:06.680
Not only that,

00:04:07.080 --> 00:04:07.800
I also know

00:04:08.000 --> 00:04:09.960
they plan to rent a warehouse in the suburbs next

00:04:10.159 --> 00:04:10.680
to stockpile goods.

00:04:11.280 --> 00:04:12.919
I also know the exact location of that warehouse,

00:04:13.159 --> 00:04:14.479
and their fleet's license plate numbers.

00:04:14.840 --> 00:04:15.560
Once I discover

00:04:15.560 --> 00:04:17.040
they start moving things into the warehouse,

00:04:17.519 --> 00:04:19.319
or contact truck drivers to prepare for shipment,

00:04:19.560 --> 00:04:20.480
I will call the police.

00:04:20.720 --> 00:04:20.920
You...

00:04:21.079 --> 00:04:22.360
get out while you can, okay?

00:04:22.519 --> 00:04:23.800
You must not follow Longshi

00:04:23.800 --> 00:04:24.600
and go down with them.

00:04:25.360 --> 00:04:26.000
Ruochu.

00:04:26.639 --> 00:04:27.360
Such a big matter,

00:04:27.759 --> 00:04:28.920
and you didn't even mention it to me.

00:04:29.519 --> 00:04:30.879
You actually wanted to shoulder it alone.

00:04:31.759 --> 00:04:33.000
Of course I have evidence to prove

00:04:33.000 --> 00:04:33.920
their dirty dealings.

00:04:34.560 --> 00:04:35.000
How about this,

00:04:35.279 --> 00:04:37.079
let's set a time to meet and talk, okay?

00:04:37.800 --> 00:04:39.120
Ruochu, come help me quick!

00:04:39.120 --> 00:04:39.480
What is it?

00:04:40.399 --> 00:04:41.360
How did you do this?

00:04:41.360 --> 00:04:42.439
Go quickly, you fix it.

00:04:42.439 --> 00:04:43.399
I'll go handle it.

00:04:43.680 --> 00:04:44.399
Hurry up and go.

00:05:03.079 --> 00:05:04.040
It's all cleaned up.

00:05:04.439 --> 00:05:05.040
I declare,

00:05:05.399 --> 00:05:07.480
you are the most virtuous wife in the world.

00:05:07.560 --> 00:05:09.120
You wasted two eggs.

00:05:09.959 --> 00:05:10.480
No way.

00:05:11.079 --> 00:05:11.800
This is too dangerous.

00:05:11.800 --> 00:05:12.399
I have to go find him.

00:05:12.399 --> 00:05:12.920
Hey, no.

00:05:13.600 --> 00:05:14.639
Chen Fan gave strict orders,

00:05:14.839 --> 00:05:16.439
saying we must guard you without leaving your side.

00:05:16.680 --> 00:05:17.879
We can't let you go no matter what.

00:05:17.879 --> 00:05:19.600
He has already gone to the meeting in your place.

00:05:42.120 --> 00:05:43.480
Give me the materials. Hurry up.

00:05:50.079 --> 00:05:50.560
Stop right there!

00:05:52.720 --> 00:05:53.399
What are you waiting for?

00:05:53.480 --> 00:05:53.920
Run, quick!

00:05:54.040 --> 00:05:54.759
Wait, wait.

00:05:55.600 --> 00:05:56.560
I was the one who asked her out.

00:05:56.920 --> 00:05:58.519
If I run, I'll look very suspicious.

00:05:58.519 --> 00:05:59.040
I'll think of a way.

00:05:59.199 --> 00:06:00.319
Go. You go first, Boss Liu.

00:06:00.319 --> 00:06:01.240
You go first. Hurry up!

00:06:07.120 --> 00:06:08.519
Is this lady injured?

00:06:09.319 --> 00:06:10.160
It was a man.

00:06:10.240 --> 00:06:11.360
Luckily you arrived in time.

00:06:11.360 --> 00:06:13.120
As soon as we received Liang Shichu's report,

00:06:13.120 --> 00:06:13.839
we rushed over here.

00:06:13.920 --> 00:06:14.160
Let's go.

00:06:14.279 --> 00:06:15.160
We happened to witness

00:06:15.160 --> 00:06:16.319
the entire process of this premeditated murder.

00:06:16.759 --> 00:06:18.199
The driver's identity has been confirmed.

00:06:18.600 --> 00:06:19.560
He's from the Longshi Group.

00:06:20.120 --> 00:06:22.360
It's not that guy named Zhou you asked me to watch.

00:06:28.079 --> 00:06:28.680
Reporting, Captain.

00:06:28.839 --> 00:06:29.839
We found another person nearby.

00:06:29.920 --> 00:06:31.360
He says the driver threatened him to come here.

00:06:31.519 --> 00:06:32.199
He was even knocked unconscious.

00:06:32.680 --> 00:06:33.600
It must be Zhou Honghai.

00:06:33.879 --> 00:06:34.759
It's definitely Zhou Honghai.

00:06:34.759 --> 00:06:35.639
Send him to the hospital first.

00:06:35.680 --> 00:06:35.920
Yes, sir.

00:06:36.800 --> 00:06:37.319
No, officer.

00:06:37.959 --> 00:06:38.639
I have text messages here.

00:06:38.920 --> 00:06:39.680
I can prove

00:06:39.680 --> 00:06:41.279
that Zhou Honghai asked Su Ruochu to meet.

00:06:41.560 --> 00:06:42.959
I can also get you the nearby surveillance footage.

00:06:43.160 --> 00:06:44.560
Alright. Please trust us.

00:06:45.079 --> 00:06:46.720
We will definitely bring the culprit to justice.

00:06:47.120 --> 00:06:48.199
If there are any further developments,

00:06:48.199 --> 00:06:48.959
I will let you know.

00:06:58.120 --> 00:06:59.639
Now for the evening news.

00:07:00.199 --> 00:07:02.279
A premeditated hit-and-run occurred in Yunhai City.

00:07:02.600 --> 00:07:04.720
Longshi Group has issued a solemn statement.

00:07:05.399 --> 00:07:06.800
Longshi Group solemnly denies

00:07:07.000 --> 00:07:09.000
any involvement in the Lakeside Road hit-and-run case.

00:07:09.560 --> 00:07:11.639
The driver involved, surnamed Li, was a temporary hire.

00:07:11.920 --> 00:07:13.800
His personal actions are unrelated to the company.

00:07:14.040 --> 00:07:16.000
His employment was terminated prior to the incident.

00:07:16.279 --> 00:07:18.759
It seems the boss behind this is making a scapegoat.

00:07:19.959 --> 00:07:22.480
The Zhou found at the scene is not a Longshi Group employee.

00:07:22.680 --> 00:07:24.240
There is no affiliation between the two parties.

00:07:24.680 --> 00:07:26.319
Longshi Group will cooperate with the investigation

00:07:26.439 --> 00:07:27.759
and pursue legal responsibility for the spreading

00:07:27.759 --> 00:07:29.199
of false rumors.

00:07:31.480 --> 00:07:32.839
Brother Honghai was really foolish.

00:07:35.160 --> 00:07:37.279
Alright, it's all in the past. Don't think about it.

00:07:37.399 --> 00:07:38.439
Why don't we think about

00:07:38.959 --> 00:07:40.519
where to go for our vacation.

00:07:54.680 --> 00:07:55.160
Mom

00:07:56.560 --> 00:07:57.120
I'm back.

00:07:57.120 --> 00:07:57.920
You must be exhausted.

00:07:58.040 --> 00:07:58.480
Not really.

00:07:59.639 --> 00:08:01.000
This is Chen Fan.

00:08:01.000 --> 00:08:01.800
He brought me home.

00:08:01.800 --> 00:08:02.439
Hello, Auntie.

00:08:03.199 --> 00:08:05.040
You're the one from the news...

00:08:05.480 --> 00:08:07.560
Chen Fan, involved in the premeditated hit-and-run?

00:08:09.639 --> 00:08:10.040
Let's go.

00:08:10.160 --> 00:08:10.639
Mom!

00:08:11.120 --> 00:08:11.959
Auntie...

00:08:12.639 --> 00:08:13.399
Mom, are you okay?

00:08:13.600 --> 00:08:14.319
I'm fine.

00:08:15.120 --> 00:08:15.519
Let's go.

00:08:22.439 --> 00:08:23.040
Are you hungry?

00:08:23.040 --> 00:08:24.240
Ruochu's mother's eyes...

00:08:25.240 --> 00:08:26.920
Have they already started to blur?

00:08:30.720 --> 00:08:31.240
Auntie.

00:08:31.600 --> 00:08:33.360
If you need anything at home, just ask me.

00:08:33.480 --> 00:08:34.080
Get out!

00:08:34.600 --> 00:08:36.480
Why come here now with your fake sympathy?

00:08:36.879 --> 00:08:39.120
You didn't take care of Ruochu when she was alive.

00:08:39.639 --> 00:08:40.600
Get out of here!

00:08:40.679 --> 00:08:42.639
Go! Go away! Go!

00:08:42.679 --> 00:08:43.080
Auntie...

00:08:43.159 --> 00:08:44.519
Leave! Go!

00:08:44.759 --> 00:08:46.000
Get out!

00:08:46.159 --> 00:08:46.720
Auntie...

00:08:46.720 --> 00:08:47.240
Don't come here again!

00:08:47.240 --> 00:08:48.559
Get out! Go!

00:08:48.759 --> 00:08:49.399
In my past life,

00:08:49.759 --> 00:08:51.120
Auntie, who already had eye trouble,

00:08:51.120 --> 00:08:53.039
cried herself blind because of Ruochu's death.

00:08:53.320 --> 00:08:53.919
In this life,

00:08:54.120 --> 00:08:55.679
I must do something for Auntie in advance.

00:09:02.879 --> 00:09:04.240
Mom, you're back.

00:09:04.240 --> 00:09:05.639
Oh, you child.

00:09:05.639 --> 00:09:07.600
It would've been so nice to go out for dinner together.

00:09:07.600 --> 00:09:08.639
Why wouldn't you come out when I asked?

00:09:09.080 --> 00:09:10.639
Mom, um...

00:09:11.159 --> 00:09:11.679
Auntie.

00:09:13.480 --> 00:09:15.360
Chen Fan, he... he...

00:09:15.360 --> 00:09:17.159
I was too abrupt yesterday and didn't bring a gift.

00:09:17.480 --> 00:09:18.879
I thought since you're busy with work,

00:09:18.879 --> 00:09:20.159
I'd cook a few dishes to nourish you.

00:09:20.159 --> 00:09:22.159
Mom, he came over early in the morning.

00:09:22.159 --> 00:09:23.279
Carrying a bunch of stuff.

00:09:23.279 --> 00:09:24.960
He waited downstairs for over three hours.

00:09:25.080 --> 00:09:26.759
In this heat, he almost got heatstroke.

00:09:27.240 --> 00:09:28.399
The neighbors all saw it.

00:09:28.559 --> 00:09:29.919
I swear I'm not lying.

00:09:31.440 --> 00:09:32.639
Um, there's one last dish.

00:09:32.639 --> 00:09:33.879
Please sit, it'll be ready in a second.

00:09:36.120 --> 00:09:36.519
Come on.

00:09:38.240 --> 00:09:40.360
Did you make all these by yourself?

00:09:40.639 --> 00:09:41.399
Yes, Mom.

00:09:41.720 --> 00:09:43.039
All the frying and cooking,

00:09:43.039 --> 00:09:44.200
washing vegetables and cleaning fish,

00:09:44.639 --> 00:09:45.639
he was busy for most of the day.

00:09:45.639 --> 00:09:47.039
I couldn't even lend a hand.

00:09:47.039 --> 00:09:48.159
It's what I should do.

00:09:48.879 --> 00:09:50.440
Well, I should learn a bit too.

00:09:50.440 --> 00:09:51.000
In the future...

00:09:51.000 --> 00:09:51.399
You don't need to.

00:09:51.720 --> 00:09:52.600
I'll handle it all from now on.

00:09:58.879 --> 00:09:59.600
Oh right, Auntie.

00:10:00.159 --> 00:10:01.360
Actually, today,

00:10:01.360 --> 00:10:02.440
the meal isn't the most important thing.

00:10:02.519 --> 00:10:03.679
I wanted to give you these.

00:10:04.039 --> 00:10:05.759
This is lutein to relieve eye fatigue.

00:10:06.240 --> 00:10:07.799
This steam eye mask is constant temperature.

00:10:07.799 --> 00:10:08.639
It feels very comfortable to wear.

00:10:09.200 --> 00:10:10.840
Most importantly, this eye massager.

00:10:11.320 --> 00:10:12.519
It can adjust the intensity

00:10:12.720 --> 00:10:13.840
and massage the acupoints around the eyes.

00:10:15.919 --> 00:10:17.879
How did you know my eyes were bothering me?

00:10:18.200 --> 00:10:20.799
I just mentioned in passing that my mom has dry eyes.

00:10:21.200 --> 00:10:22.480
Why did you buy so many things?

00:10:22.600 --> 00:10:23.879
Small problems need attention too.

00:10:24.159 --> 00:10:24.879
We can't be careless.

00:10:39.399 --> 00:10:40.639
I'll keep them for now.

00:10:40.639 --> 00:10:41.320
Let's eat.

00:10:41.879 --> 00:10:42.240
Let's eat.

00:10:42.240 --> 00:10:42.879
Taste this.